eight="193" class="float-none" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" alt="Select the service"></p><p>Click the correct service listed in your invoice.Â If you are paying for multiple invoices, please contact Ms. Hanna at (+65) 8355 1210</p></div></div><div id="rlta-step-3-select-the-service-country" role="button" aria-controls="rlta-panel-step-3-select-the-service-country" aria-expanded="false" tabindex="0" data-rlta-alias="step-3-select-the-service-country" data-rlta-element="button" data-rlta-state="closed"><div data-rlta-element="heading"> Step 3: Select the service country.</div></div><div id="rlta-panel-step-3-select-the-service-country" aria-labelledby="rlta-step-3-select-the-service-country" tabindex="-1" hidden="true" data-rlta-element="panel" data-rlta-state="closed" data-rlta-color="false"><div data-rlta-element="panel-content"><p data-start="1020" data-end="1263" class=""><img src="https://globallinkconsulting.sg/images/2025/04/select-the-country.png" width="700" height="96" class="float-none" alt="Select the country" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"></p><p data-start="1020" data-end="1263" class="">Choose the country related to your service. For example, if you're paying for a Singapore company setup, choose "Singapore". For offshore, US, Hong Kong, etc., select "Other countries".</p></div></div><div id="rlta-step-4-choose-your-preferred-payment-method" role="button" aria-controls="rlta-panel-step-4-choose-your-preferred-payment-method" aria-expanded="false" tabindex="0" data-rlta-alias="step-4-choose-your-preferred-payment-method" data-rlta-element="button" data-rlta-state="closed"><div data-rlta-element="heading"> Step 4: Choose your preferred payment method.</div></div><div id="rlta-panel-step-4-choose-your-preferred-payment-method" aria-labelledby="rlta-step-4-choose-your-preferred-payment-method" tabindex="-1" hidden="true" data-rlta-element="panel" data-rlta-state="closed" data-rlta-color="fals